...the other one is a new song written by Shota Horie.

716
00:46:20,139 --> 00:46:21,639
２曲も？新曲？
Two songs? New songs?

717
00:46:21,739 --> 00:46:24,539
そうなんです、２曲も新曲がここで！
That's right, two new songs right here!

718
00:46:24,639 --> 00:46:26,639
人に委ねたんだねー
Entrusted them to people, huh?

719
00:46:26,739 --> 00:46:28,939
そうなんですよー。ありがとうございます
Exactly. Thank you.

720
00:46:29,339 --> 00:46:33,839
ということでね、どちらも強いメッセージ性のある楽曲に仕上がってるとのことです
And so, both of them are said to be songs with a strong message.

721
00:46:33,939 --> 00:46:35,239
２曲！
Two songs!

722
00:46:35,339 --> 00:46:37,239
今日一のびっくりですね、ポルカさん
That's the biggest surprise of the day, Polka.

723
00:46:37,439 --> 00:46:39,339
はい。それでは参りましょう
Yes. Well then, let's get to it.

724
00:46:39,439 --> 00:46:42,039
DECO*27さん書き下ろし曲、『ばかばっか』
A song written by DECO*27, "Baka Bakka."

725
00:46:42,139 --> 00:46:45,339
堀江晶太さん書き下ろし曲、『First Cry』
A song written by Shota Horie, "First Cry."

726
00:46:45,739 --> 00:46:48,139
２曲続けてどうぞ！
Please listen to the two songs in a row!

727
00:46:48,239 --> 00:46:48,839
どうぞ！
Go ahead!

728
00:46:52,839 --> 00:46:56,839
ばかばっか / 作詞・作曲: DECO*27
Baka Bakka / Lyrics and Composition: DECO*27

729
